# Cloudflare Pages routing — SPA fallback.
#
# Maree is a pure client-rendered Vite SPA (no prerendered pages). CF Pages
# serves real static files first (assets, splash.html); this catch-all sends
# every other path to the app shell with a 200 so client-side routes resolve
# instead of 404ing.
#
# Replaces the Vercel `rewrites: /(.*) -> /index.html` config. Clean URLs are
# native on CF, so no cleanUrls equivalent is needed.
/*    /index.html   200
